## Brute Force (For Understanding)

```java
class Solution {

    public boolean checkIfExist(int[] arr) {

        for (int i = 0; i < arr.length; i++) {

            for (int j = 0; j < arr.length; j++) {

                if (i != j && arr[i] == 2 * arr[j]) {
                    return true;
                }
            }
        }

        return false;
    }
}
```

### Brute Force Complexity

* **Time Complexity:** `O(n²)`
* **Space Complexity:** `O(1)`

